---
title: Cheeseburger-Style Beef Quesadillas with Caramelised Onion & Charred Corn Salsa
description: Go stateside tonight by adding southern American flavours to a beef filling for quesadillas with a touch of Dijon mustard, so
when you close your eyes, it tastes just like a cheeseburger! Sneak some veggies into the mix, smother the lot with cheese, top it
off with sticky caramelised onion and you're good to go. That's all, folks!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheeseburger-style-beef-quesadillas-442e408e.jpg
